  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      143.85,
      280.87,
      383.93,
      305.61
    ],
    "text": "BE it enacted by the Parliament of the Democratic SocialistRepublic of Sri Lanka as follows:\u2014",
    "fonts": [
      "Times-Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      143.85,
      315.07,
      383.88,
      339.81
    ],
    "text": "1.This Act may be cited as the Gramodaya MandalaFund (Amendment) Act, No. 68 of 2009.",
    "fonts": [
      "Times-Bold",
      "Times-Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      143.85,
      349.27,
      383.97,
      408.21
    ],
    "text": "2.The Long Title to the Gramodaya Mandala Fund Act,No. 28 of 1982 (hereinafter referred to as the \u201cprincipalenactment\u201d) is hereby amended by the substitution for thewords \u201cGramodaya Mandala Fund\u201d of the words \u201cJana DiriyaFund\u201d.",
    "fonts": [
      "Times-Bold",
      "Times-Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      143.85,
      417.67,
      384.03,
      476.61
    ],
    "text": "3.(1) In the principal enactment and in any other writtenlaw, there shall be substituted for the words \u201cGramodayaMandala Fund Act\u201d and \u201cGramodaya Mandala Fund,\u201d of thewords \u201cJana Diriya Fund Act\u201d and \u201cJana Diriya Fund\u201d,respectively.",
    "fonts": [
      "Times-Bold",
      "Times-Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      143.85,
      486.07,
      383.85,
      545.01
    ],
    "text": "(2) Every reference to the \u201cGramodaya Mandala FundAct\u201d and \u201cGramodaya Mandala Fund\u201d in any regulation,rule, order, notice, notification or other document shall beread and construed as a reference to the \u201cJana Diriya FundAct\u201d and the \u201cJana Diriya Fund\u201d, respectively.",
    "fonts": [
      "Times-Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      143.85,
      554.47,
      383.9,
      579.21
    ],
